Former Manchester United forward Bebe has defended Cristiano Ronaldo after his sending off against Cordoba in La Liga on Saturday, insisting it could have happened to anyone.

The Real Madrid star lost his cool as he endured a frustrating afternoon and was sent off for kicking Edimar Fraga with the game level at 1-1.

Ronaldo could have been given his marching orders sooner had the referee spotted his attempted punch on Jose Crespo as the Ballon d'Or winner's temper boiled over. 

