In one final act of petulance Ronaldo aimed a back-handed swipe at Crespo following the incident involving Fraga. 

But Bebe, who is on loan at Cordoba from Portuguese side Benfica, has given his compatriot a glowing character reference and explained anyone could crack under the pressure of such an intense moment.

'Cristiano has already apologised,' he told AS after the match.

'It is something that could have happened to anyone. It has happened to me and to many other players that I know. 

